import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.scatter(data['longitude'], data['latitude'], s=10, alpha=0.5)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of longitude and latitude?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Longitude')
    plt.ylabel('Latitude')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['speed'], bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.7)
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['speed'].mean():0.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['speed'].median():0.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Speed')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of speed?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['dirCat'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', color='blue')
    plt.title('How does the direction of travel vary across the dataset?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Direction Category')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['dirCat'] = pd.Categorical(data['dir'])
    data['dirCat'] = data['dirCat'].cat.codes
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.scatter(data['speed'], data['dirCat'], alpha=0.5)
    ax.set_xlabel('Speed')
    ax.set_ylabel('Direction')
    ax.set_yticks(data['dirCat'].unique())
    ax.set_yticklabels(data['dir'].unique())
    plt.title('What is the relationship between speed and direction?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['speed'] = pd.to_numeric(data['speed'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['speed'])
    avg_speed = data.groupby('dirCat')['speed'].mean().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))
    ax.bar(avg_speed['dirCat'], avg_speed['speed'], color='blue')
    ax.set_xlabel('Direction Category')
    ax.set_ylabel('Average Speed')
    ax.set_title('What is the average speed for each direction category?')
    plt.show()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
